HEADWORD: Transmigrant
<hw>Trans"mi*grant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>transmigrans</ets>, p. pr. See <er>Transmigrate</er>.]</ety>
<def>Migrating or passing from one place or state to another; passing
from one residence to another.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
transmigrates.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

